OpenCurrent v1.1

Please see http://code.google.com/p/opencurrent/ for documentation and build instructions.

This project is built with CMake, v2.6.4 or later.

OpenCurrent has the following dependencies:

CMake v2.6.4 or later  http://www.cmake.org/
CUDA 2.3 or later      http://www.nvidia.com/object/cuda_get.html
(Optional) NetCDF v3.6 or later   http://www.unidata.ucar.edu/software/netcdf/

NVIDIA Display drivers 190 or later are required (for CUDA 2.3 compatibility).  


OpenCurrent has been tested on Windows XP 32 bit and Ubuntu 64 bit.  CUDA 2.3 and CUDA 3.0.

